entities.name: arithmetic-combinator
entities.player_description:
[virtual-signal=signal-P] = base priority
[item=red-wire][virtual-signal=signal-L] = number of full deliveries this station can provide
Sets priority to [item=red-wire][virtual-signal=signal-L]+[virtual-signal=signal-P]

entities.name: arithmetic-combinator
entities.player_description:
[virtual-signal=signal-stack-size] = number of full stacks stored in buffer
[virtual-signal=signal-C] = calculated train cargo capacity in stacks
[virtual-signal=signal-L] = number of full deliveries this station can provide

Calculates [virtual-signal=signal-L]

entities.name: arithmetic-combinator
entities.player_description:
Sum full stacks of each item in buffer.
Output as [virtual-signal=signal-stack-size]

entities.name: constant-combinator
entities.player_description:
[virtual-signal=signal-W] = cargo wagons
[virtual-signal=signal-S] = cargo wagon slots
[virtual-signal=signal-W]*[virtual-signal=signal-S]=[virtual-signal=signal-C] = total train cargo capacity
[virtual-signal=signal-P] = base priority
